{
  "uid": "grob-overview",
  "title": "Grob — Observabilité technique",
  "tags": ["grob", "llm", "proxy"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "10s",
  "time": { "from": "now-30m", "to": "now" },
  "links": [
    {
      "type": "link",
      "title": "Vue RSSI",
      "url": "/d/grob-rssi-business/grob-decision-rssi-ia?orgId=1",
      "icon": "external link",
      "includeVars": false,
      "keepTime": true,
      "targetBlank": false
    },
    {
      "type": "link",
      "title": "Audit agent",
      "url": "/d/grob-audit-agent/grob-audit-agent?orgId=1&var-tenant=compta-bot",
      "icon": "external link",
      "includeVars": false,
      "keepTime": true,
      "targetBlank": false
    }
  ],
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "provider",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
        "query": { "query": "label_values(grob_requests_total, provider)", "refId": "A" },
        "includeAll": true,
        "multi": true,
        "current": { "text": "All", "value": "$__all" }
      },
      {
        "name": "model",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
        "query": { "query": "label_values(grob_requests_total, model)", "refId": "A" },
        "includeAll": true,
        "multi": true,
        "current": { "text": "All", "value": "$__all" }
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1, "type": "stat", "title": "Requêtes totales",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "color": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "blue" } } },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area" },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "expr": "sum(grob_requests_total{provider=~\"$provider\", model=~\"$model\"})" } ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2, "type": "stat", "title": "Débit requêtes",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 0 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "reqps", "color": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "green" } } },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area" },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "expr": "sum(rate(grob_requests_total{provider=~\"$provider\", model=~\"$model\"}[$__rate_interval]))" } ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3, "type": "stat", "title": "Requêtes en cours",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 0 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "thresholds": { "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": null }, { "color": "yellow", "value": 20 }, { "color": "red", "value": 50 } ] } } },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "area" },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "expr": "sum(grob_active_requests)" } ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4, "type": "stat", "title": "Latence p95",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 0 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "ms", "thresholds": { "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": null }, { "color": "yellow", "value": 200 }, { "color": "red", "value": 500 } ] } } },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "area" },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "expr": "max(grob_request_duration_seconds{provider=~\"$provider\", model=~\"$model\", quantile=\"0.95\"}) * 1000" } ]
    },
    {
      "id": 10, "type": "timeseries", "title": "Débit par modèle",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "reqps", "custom": { "fillOpacity": 20, "stacking": { "mode": "normal" }, "lineWidth": 1 } } },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "expr": "sum by (model) (rate(grob_requests_total{provider=~\"$provider\", model=~\"$model\"}[$__rate_interval]))", "legendFormat": "{{model}}" } ]
    },
    {
      "id": 11, "type": "timeseries", "title": "Débit par provider",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "reqps", "custom": { "fillOpacity": 20, "stacking": { "mode": "normal" }, "lineWidth": 1 } } },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "expr": "sum by (provider) (rate(grob_requests_total{provider=~\"$provider\", model=~\"$model\"}[$__rate_interval]))", "legendFormat": "{{provider}}" } ]
    },
    {
      "id": 12, "type": "timeseries", "title": "Latence p50 / p95 / p99",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 12 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "ms", "custom": { "fillOpacity": 10, "lineWidth": 2 } } },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "max(grob_request_duration_seconds{provider=~\"$provider\", model=~\"$model\", quantile=\"0.5\"}) * 1000", "legendFormat": "p50" },
        { "refId": "B", "expr": "max(grob_request_duration_seconds{provider=~\"$provider\", model=~\"$model\", quantile=\"0.95\"}) * 1000", "legendFormat": "p95" },
        { "refId": "C", "expr": "max(grob_request_duration_seconds{provider=~\"$provider\", model=~\"$model\", quantile=\"0.99\"}) * 1000", "legendFormat": "p99" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 13, "type": "timeseries", "title": "Résultats par statut",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 12 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "reqps", "custom": { "fillOpacity": 30, "stacking": { "mode": "normal" }, "lineWidth": 1 } } },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "expr": "sum by (status) (rate(grob_requests_total{provider=~\"$provider\", model=~\"$model\"}[$__rate_interval]))", "legendFormat": "{{status}}" } ]
    },
    {
      "id": 20, "type": "timeseries", "title": "Erreurs provider / s",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 20 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "custom": { "fillOpacity": 20, "lineWidth": 1 }, "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" } } },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "expr": "sum(rate(grob_provider_errors_total[$__rate_interval])) or vector(0)", "legendFormat": "errors/s" } ]
    },
    {
      "id": 21, "type": "timeseries", "title": "Tokens / s",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 8, "y": 20 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "custom": { "fillOpacity": 10, "lineWidth": 2 } } },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "sum(rate(grob_input_tokens_total{provider=~\"$provider\", model=~\"$model\"}[$__rate_interval]))", "legendFormat": "input" },
        { "refId": "B", "expr": "sum(rate(grob_output_tokens_total{provider=~\"$provider\", model=~\"$model\"}[$__rate_interval]))", "legendFormat": "output" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 22, "type": "bargauge", "title": "Dépense et budget",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 20 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "currencyUSD", "thresholds": { "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": null }, { "color": "yellow", "value": 0.5 }, { "color": "red", "value": 0.9 } ] } } },
      "options": { "orientation": "horizontal", "displayMode": "gradient", "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] } },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "sum(grob_spend_usd)", "legendFormat": "spend" },
        { "refId": "B", "expr": "max(grob_budget_limit_usd)", "legendFormat": "budget limit" },
        { "refId": "C", "expr": "max(grob_budget_remaining_usd)", "legendFormat": "remaining" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 30, "type": "logs", "title": "Audit signé Loki",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 28 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
      "options": { "showTime": true, "wrapLogMessage": true, "enableLogDetails": true, "sortOrder": "Descending", "dedupStrategy": "none", "prettifyLogMessage": false },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" }, "expr": "{service=\"grob-audit\"}" } ]
    },
    {
      "id": 31, "type": "table", "title": "Traces Tempo",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 38 },
      "datasource": { "type": "tempo", "uid": "tempo" },
      "options": { "showHeader": true },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "datasource": { "type": "tempo", "uid": "tempo" }, "queryType": "traceql", "query": "{ resource.service.name = \"grob\" }", "limit": 20 } ]
    },
    {
      "id": 32, "type": "text", "title": "Corrélation Loki vers Tempo",
      "gridPos": { "h": 9, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 48 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "Cette démo instrumente **grob** et pousse l'audit signé dans **Loki**. Chaque ligne d'audit porte `trace_id` et `span_id`; Tempo expose le span `http_request` correspondant.\n\nLe **service graph** Tempo est absent dans cette topologie : le fournisseur de démo est un mock nginx non instrumenté, donc Tempo ne voit pas de second service ni d'arête inter-service. Pour la preuve, ouvrez une ligne Loki, copiez `trace_id`, puis retrouvez le span dans **Traces Tempo**."
      }
    }
  ]
}
